#- 1. Why The Ancaps§0
§0exist.§0
§0
§0Long, long ago. Ttk§0
§0made a server called§0
§0'ancapminecraft'.§0
§0It was a server§0
§0created because ttk§0
§0was getting bullied by§0
§0leftists server hosts.§0

#- Ancapminecraft was a§0
§0Haven for all edgy§0
§0teenagers that hate§0
§0equality and actual§0
§0liberty.§0
§0
§0Notorious ancaps that§0
§0joined this server are§0
§0Joshua97367 and§0
§0FoxmcLeod.§0

#- Then a prophet of§0
§0freedom and solidarity§0
§0joined ancapminecraft.§0
§0They started a guild§0
§0of solidarity and§0
§0equality called "The§0
§0LibSoc Guild"§0
§0
§0Ttk was baffeled and§0
§0coaxed that some§0
§0leftist pussy could§0
§0come over to his§0
§0server.§0

#- The LibSoc Guild§0
§0ruined his server.§0
§0And ttk used...§0
§0
§0... the terminal.§0
§0
§0And CivCraft was born.§0

#- 2. The Free Baby§0
§0Market§0
§0
§0The Ancaps didn't§0
§0spread much in the§0
§0beginning of CivCraft,§0
§0they made a vagina§0
§0shaft called 'The Rift'.§0
§0
§0The Ancap virus was§0
§0contianed, and all was§0
§0well.§0

#- Some Leftist freedom§0
§0fighters decided to§0
§0get rid of the§0
§0oppression and racism§0
§0once and for all.§0
§0They burned The Rift§0
§0and destroyed the§0
§0Ancaps menace.§0
§0
§0People thought the§0
§0Ancap virus had been§0
§0eradicated, but it was§0
§0far from that...§0

#- The Ancaps spread to§0
§0once free cities such§0
§0as Columbia and§0
§0Augusta, and§0
§0destroyed them from§0
§0inside out.§0
§0
§0Foofed "Gatzy"§0
§0Timmyius went into the§0
§0democratic leftist§0
§0parliament and§0
§0dissolved it.§0

#- Oppression and racism§0
§0ran rampant, and then§0
§0the Free Baby Market§0
§0started.§0
§0
§0The Free Baby Market§0
§0consists of inner§0
§0hierarchies.§0

#- The Hierarchies are:§0
§0
§01. Foofed§0
§02.§0
§0Matticus_Fucking_Rex§0
