§0the penis towers are§0
§0modeled after.§0
§0The Free Baby Market§0
§0is made to oppress§0
§0free, leftist people.§0
§0And make people racist§0
§0and hateful.§0

#- The Free Baby§0
§0Markets sells Babies§0
