#- 2a. The Monopoly on§0
§0Force and Justice§0
§0
§0The Ancaps hate§0
§0freedom, even though§0
§0they act like they want§0
§0personal freedom.§0
§0They disregard§0
§0legitamite state rules§0
§0and just run into§0
§0free, sovreign nations§0
§0and torment their§0
§0inhabitants.§0

#- They kill anybody§0
§0trying to interfere§0
§0with their "justice"§0
§0and then they tell§0
§0everybody that they§0
§0are against§0
§0"Monopolies on Force"§0
§0but they kill§0
§0everybody without§0
§0care.§0
§0They know who to not§0
§0kill by using their§0
§0secret device;§0

#- 3. The CKC§0
§0
§0The CKC is a cesspool§0
§0of crime and§0
§0corruption, it's where§0
§0the Ancaps go to§0
§0oppress free,§0
§0beautiful people.§0
§0They talk to eachother§0
§0about the definition of§0
§0definition and air, and§0
§0how to oppress§0
§0leftists more evil.§0

#- In their free time The§0
